text: Nurlino () is a rural locality (a selo) in Nikolayevsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,892 as of 2010. There are 32 streets. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Ufa, 8 km from Nikolayevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Nurlino
